The evidence with the title 'Trump's case against the Iran nuclear deal has very little to do with ... ' says Sep 13, 2017  ... When you hear the Trump administration talk about Iran , then, it doesn't tend to focus very much on the threat from Tehran 's nuclear program. Instead, it tends to talk about Iran 's broader policies toward the Middle East. Iran “ is responsible for so much instability , ” the president said in a may 2017 speech. 
